        <message>You can find your leave balance on [Workday](https://wd3.myworkday.com/absa/d/home.htmld): 
1. Click on the cloud icon or your profile picture and select **view profile** from the drop-down list.
2. Underneath your name and surname on the left of your screen, click on **Time off**.
3. Select **Time Off Balance**.
4. Click on **View Time Off Balance**.
5. All types of leave will appear. Your balance can be seen as **Accumulated Leave**.</message>
